<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <script src="https://public.tableau.com/javascripts/api/viz_v1.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f6f3;
        }

        .content-wrapper {
            margin-top: 80px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .dashboard-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .dashboard-buttons button {
            background-color: #a63636;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .dashboard-buttons button:hover {
            background-color: #8c2e2e;
        }

        iframe {
            width: 100%;
            height: 800px;
            border: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h1>About Turtle Shelter Project</h1>
        <p>
            The <strong>Turtle Shelter Project</strong> was born from a desire to protect those experiencing homelessness from the harsh realities of the cold. 
            Every year, extreme weather conditions claim the lives of individuals without access to proper shelter and clothing.
        </p>
        <p>
            Inspired by the resilience and adaptability of turtles, our vests are designed to be lightweight, portable, and incredibly effective. 
            With the help of compassionate volunteers, donors, and community support, we've distributed thousands of vests and saved countless lives. 
            Together, we can continue to make a difference.
        </p>

        <h2>Explore Homelessness Statistics</h2>
        <p>Switch between Utah-specific and National data to understand homelessness trends and insights.</p>
        <div class="dashboard-container">
            <div class="dashboard-buttons">
                <button onclick="showDashboard('utah')">Utah Data</button>
                <button onclick="showDashboard('national')">National Data</button>
            </div>
            <iframe id="dashboard" src="https://public.tableau.com/views/NationalDashboard/NationalDashbaord" title="Homelessness Dashboard"></iframe>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script>
        function showDashboard(type) {
            const iframe = document.getElementById('dashboard');
            if (type === 'utah') {
                iframe.src = 'https://public.tableau.com/views/NationalDashboard/UtahDashboard';
            } else if (type === 'national') {
                iframe.src = 'https://public.tableau.com/views/NationalDashboard/NationalDashbaord';
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>
